divs: sighting detailsover 6 hours of many, many activities.cars lifted away, unconscience people found in cars, item "taken" out of my car. 2 beings standing\hovering in front of me. cloud full of tiny lightning, fireball, one of the mother ships " tricked" me as i followed it in my car. all in all, a very long story which i am not able to put all into writing at this time. would be willing to discuss in person.
